1. Usage
      ./logging.sh tablenumber
2. Synopsis
      The gamelog of the table given by tablenumber is extracted an processed to get a single line summary of the games played.
      Useful for extracting game related informations from www.liveplayok.com The downloaded files are stored in a user specified
      directory. These files are tar zipped and stored after the relevant informations are extracted.
3. Dependencies
      Standard linux tools + bidstring + shortnames
      
      bidstring can be obtained by running
      g++ -o bidstring bidstring.cpp
      shortnames
      g++ -o shortnames shortnames.cpp